.parallax.parallax-wildlife{ data: { center: 'background-position:0px 0px;', top: { bottom: 'background-position: 0px 400px;' }  }, style: 'background-position: 0px 0px;' }
%section#wildlife.container.content-section
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
      %h2.text-center Wildlife

      %p
        The particular habitat of the Chinko allows for an incredible richness of species,
        and puzzling phenomena, making it a hotspot of biodiversity.



      %p
        #wildlife-carousel.owl-carousel
          - %w(african-wild-dog african-elephant lord-derby-eland giant-forest-hog lelwel-hartebeest leopard).each do |name|
            .image
              = image_tag('wildlife/'+ name +'.jpg')
              .image-description
                = name.titleize

        :javascript
          $(document).ready(function(){
            $("#wildlife-carousel").owlCarousel({
                items: 1,
                loop: true,
                margin: 10,
                lazyLoad: true,
                merge: true,
                video: true
              });
          });

      %p
        So far we've documented more than 75 mammals (including Wild Dog, Elephant, Lelwel
        Hartebeest, Eastern Giant Eland, Bongo, Lion and Leopard).

      %p.text-center
        %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{href: "http://research.chinkoproject.com"}
          > 70,000 Photos
        %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{href: "http://research.chinkoproject.com/species_list"}
          > 75 mammals
        %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{href: "http://research.chinkoproject.com/publications"}
          > 8 publications
